      <title>对冲基金 Walleye 解雇十几名员工，包括股权资本市场主管</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/hedge-fund-walleye-dismisses-a-dozen-staff-including-ecm-head</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，对冲基金 Walleye Capital 已裁减约十几个职位，包括股权资本市场主管。]]></description>
