    <item>
      <title>嘉能可腐败调查以瑞士罚款结束</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/glencore-ordered-to-pay-150-million-by-swiss-in-criminal-probe</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞士当局结束对这家大宗商品交易商和矿业公司的调查后，嘉能可公司将支付 1.52 亿美元，这标志着欧洲和美洲长达六年多的法律调查结束。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/glencore-ordered-to-pay-150-million-by-swiss-in-criminal-probe</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 12:26:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
